Name: massnotice
Author: n00bie
Category: Other
Last updated: 2006-11-29T17:14:24+00:00

[b]Description:[/b]

This module will make services clients (ChanServ, NickServ, BotServ, HostServ, MemoServ, HelpServ, OperServ) sends a mass notice to all users on the network.
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
[b]Providing Commands:[/b]

/msg ChanServ MNOTICE [message]
/msg NickServ MNOTICE [message]
/msg BotServ  MNOTICE [message]
/msg HostServ MNOTICE [message]
/msg MemoServ MNOTICE [message]
/msg HelpServ MNOTICE [message]
/msg OperServ MNOTICE [message]

and

/msg ChanServ HELP MNOTICE 
etc..
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
[b]NOTE:[/b] Commands is limited to Services Admins & above.

This module have no configurable option.

Version 1.0.0 supports Anope 1.7.18
Version 2.0.0 supports Anope 1.7.21
